title: The ornamental projection, including the voids, flower beds, etc
clause_text: The ornamental projection, including the voids, flower beds, etc. projecting from the face of the building except at the terrace level other than allowed as per Regulation No 31(1) (ii).
section: The following shall be counted in FSI.
